# Coffee Shop Challenge

## Description
This is a coffee shop management application that demonstrates the use of classes, object relationships, and basic CRUD operations.

## Learning Goals
- Create and manipulate Ruby classes and objects
- Understand and implement object relationships
- Practice working with arrays and hashes
- Implement basic CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations

## Classes
- `Customer`: Represents a coffee shop customer
- `Drink`: Represents a drink available at the coffee shop
- `Order`: Manages the relationships between customers and drinks

## Features
- Create new customers and drinks
- Place orders
- View order history
- Calculate total sales
- Track customer preferences

